# Self Check

Before finalizing any output — code, documentation, or configuration — verify the following.

Confirm that the implementation matches the acceptance criteria in `apps/zarya-tg/docs/prd.md` for the relevant user story (or the ticket AC under `apps/zarya-tg/docs/tickets/`). Confirm that the change matches the ticket/spec **Human summary** with no silent scope creep. Confirm that no features outside MVP scope have been added without a corresponding decision record in `apps/zarya-tg/docs/decisions/`. Confirm that user-facing text is in Russian and code comments are in English. Confirm that no secrets or credentials are included in the output. Confirm that required checks from `process/ai-factory/CI.md` were run (tests / lint / build; Railway log scan when configured). Confirm that a separate review pass was requested when finishing a ticket. Confirm that the next step is clear and actionable.

It is better to flag an uncertainty explicitly than to silently paper over it.
